    "In Sect. 7, we summarize this investigation and discuss the next steps.",
    "MethodThe goal of this investigation is two-fold: (i) to integrate a generative AI tool into a pipeline for synthetizing biomedical narratives in German and (ii) to fine-tune existing transformer-based language model for recognizing biomedical entities in medical narratives written in German.",
